    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Monthly report, quarterly review, refined as you grow.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:70ch;">Management reporting is a rhythm, not a one-off build &mdash; a monthly report that lands on schedule, a quarterly business review that turns the numbers into strategy, and a metric set that evolves with the business.</p>
    <div class="r-3">
