    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Reviewed by the ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>This page reflects how TechBrot delivers KPI and management reporting. It is maintained by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, a Delaware-incorporated independent ProAdvisor firm, and reviewed for accuracy on metric selection, leading and lagging indicators, and the boundaries of the service.</p>
      <p>Where our approach or scope changes, this page is updated. Reporting is delivered on accurate books and coordinated with your CPA for anything requiring a license. Independent firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row" style="margin-top:22px;">
      {%- for r in operatorSpec %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value">{{ r.value | safe }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ r.label | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed" style="margin-top:18px;"><span>Published: 2026-06-15</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-15</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-15 &middot; QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

